{"tid":634341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍是「中国の犬」","createTime":"2018-04-19T06:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T09:16:22.000Z","uid":111002,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d93e7d570107fbbbc908c2cc5b6321233183af78","tid":634341,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"終於有日本媒體肯屌鳩成龍條垃圾了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mag2.com/p/news/357019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mag2.com%2Fp%2Fnews%2F357019&d=nPILxhq6DeS547KB659Hb%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=015a2df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mag2.com/p/news/357019</a><br />\n<br />\n//台灣旅日作家兼時事評論員黃文雄，就早前的香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮中黃秋生的發言，帶出香港電影界以至香港人對此人的反感。從近期「沒有香港電影、只有中國電影」，到「中國人是要被管的」，再申延至民進黨第一次執政時說過「不會去台灣」...等等的言行，都有清晰的解說。<br />\n<br />\n文中提到在沒有創作言論自由的中國，藝人被錢收買，創作「官製文化」，成為統戰機器一部份。有人更當上政協之位，形容他是「中国の犬」。<br />\n不過文中並未提及此人的私德問題，否則會更精彩。//<br />\n<br />\n來源：Samantha&rsquo;s Select<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/samanthaselect/posts/1671885639569972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsamanthaselect%2Fposts%2F1671885639569972&d=nPILxhq6DeS547KB659Hb%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6b75f3c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/samanthaselect/posts/1671885639569972</a>"},{"pid":"6a560a0f44e6c5c929d0f5a2b35d396221376fed","tid":634341,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425d09db85af25a69e3d3922cb78907a84133fba","tid":634341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866321a0a77296cf9b51169fa61380d71ced2c83","tid":634341,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:11:09.000Z","msg